zi,k 


‚Ä¢ we come back to step 1 until convergence. 
Remark : The step of minimization with respect to z is equivalent to allocating the xi in 
the Voronoi cells which centers are the Œºk. 

Remark : During the step of minimization with respect to Œº, Œºk is obtained by setting to 
zero the k‚àíth coordinate of the gradient of J with respect to Œº. Indeed we can easily see 
that : rŒºk 
